{"tid":383526,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【柒到喊】澳門掛左一號波？ 皇家香港天文台：吹歪左，遲D先掛","createTime":"2017-09-01T14:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T00:58:55.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b36b782dde5297902a2c79ea2840e5a1748b0b8","tid":383526,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:19:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">澳門</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.smg.gov.mo/smg/severeWeather/c_typhoon_main.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.smg.gov.mo%2Fsmg%2FsevereWeather%2Fc_typhoon_main.htm&d=jNqal1Y62jF460GvPJUSj5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=dce126ae\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.smg.gov.mo/smg/severeWeather/c_typhoon_main.htm</a><br />\n一號風球仍然懸掛。 <br />\n在 22 時熱帶風暴 &ldquo;瑪娃&rdquo; (1716) 集結在本澳東南偏東約 520 公里，大致趨向廣東東岸。  預料一號風球將維持一段時間。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">皇家香港天文台</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1001507/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1001507%2F&d=jNqal1Y62jF460GvPJUSj5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=44e0f2c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1001507%2F&h=187554c3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1001507/</a><br />\n<br />\n「瑪娃」稍後或掛1號波 天文台調弱風力東調路徑<br />\n2017-09-01 11:48<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170901/_2017090111515850540.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170901%2F_2017090111515850540.jpg&h=b4a2aab0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天文台今日稍後考慮發出一號戒備信號，預料熱帶氣旋「瑪娃」初時移動緩慢，未來一兩日會大致移向廣東東部，該區天氣漸轉不穩定，有狂風大驟雨。<br />\n<br />\n相比今早的天氣預報，天文台最新預測的字眼亦有改變，由「隨後會逐漸移向廣東東部至珠江口一帶」，改為「未來一兩日會大致移向廣東東部」，意味路徑靠向東邊，有進一步東調空間。<br />\n<br />\n至於風力方面，天文台亦有所調弱。最新預測瑪娃周日最接近本港，風級由今早的「西北風5級，漸轉西南風6至7級」改為「西北風6級，離岸間中7級，漸轉西南風」，即平均風速每小時41至51公里，屬於三號強風信號的風級。<br />\n<br />\n天氣密雲，有狂風大驟雨及雷暴。氣溫介乎26至29度。下周一仍然多雲，有驟雨及幾陣狂風雷暴。<br />\n<br />\n正午12時，「瑪娃」集結在東沙之東南偏東約210公里，預料緩慢移動，在南海東北部徘徊。天文台預測明日有幾陣驟雨。初時短暫時間有陽光及有煙霞，稍後驟雨增多及有雷暴。氣溫介乎27至31度。<br />\n<br />\n隨著副熱帶高壓脊在下周中期增強，中國東南部天色將會好轉。下周二部分時間有陽光，有幾陣驟雨。周三大致天晴。最高氣溫回升至32度。之後數日部分時間有陽光，有幾陣驟雨。"},{"pid":"a69ca1cba8f4b4c131119c0def6dd76291e45a32","tid":383526,"uid":36238,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:31:02.000Z","msg":"柒得過D連登仔"},{"pid":"7191be99b860d201d9a7e0bb89e37d4de3800506","tid":383526,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:31:36.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"24015848b9a14476bb0f5507fdffc7be0a893bd1","tid":383526,"uid":14392,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:34:53.000Z","msg":"你唔係重信天文台呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537ecc276501c6b9d3232cbb0a6ec7b00d25f46d","tid":383526,"uid":7699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:36:36.000Z","msg":"好少澳門掛得仲早過香港 係咪驚到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7263ae5a67a99a4c8a0f46af7e255d8467ce7c","tid":383526,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:38:25.000Z","msg":"掛又死唔掛又死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5870fced7b2151e96e7874be17c73c6326e38495","tid":383526,"uid":1049,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:53:08.000Z","msg":"澳門天文台真係斷鳩估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完美演繹數據鳩睇，政治性掛風球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80c1b7b49ceb237b9fa0a453652dc47119be088","tid":383526,"uid":137627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:55:58.000Z","msg":"亂7咁黎，掛左先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"578892af5738c683896418be5438de664eae690b","tid":383526,"uid":20659,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:56:35.000Z","msg":"依家支那佔領左香港<br />\n皇家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea2f6c8b611ccc76d4bfa7326b51869b082058d","tid":383526,"uid":109102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T15:58:28.000Z","msg":"皇家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a197f4b4bb84569dc7e45f3a71e70be87aaa941d","tid":383526,"uid":103230,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T16:00:44.000Z","msg":"為左笑澳門抬高香港大交合咩玩法"},{"pid":"1895d20f9903cc598d6313cbdd5571d8d3cc2f0c","tid":383526,"uid":51584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T16:03:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>為左笑澳門抬高香港大交合咩玩法</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad55e1e3ada305f0b9cf7084ceb8f82b24f9919a","tid":383526,"uid":12757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T16:07:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>為左笑澳門抬高香港大交合咩玩法</blockquote><br />\n笑撚左班垃圾澳狗先<br />\n遲下屌柒大交合都未遲"},{"pid":"3f32d531c85dfc930c8be77499fd4d438ec1ee73","tid":383526,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T16:07:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你唔係重信天文台呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n南海之王你估流架"},{"pid":"af1a103bc3d5e084aec1d12b2e356dbd4f7fe2b3","tid":383526,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T16:09:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>為左笑澳門抬高香港大交合咩玩法</blockquote><br />\n笑撚左班垃圾澳狗先<br />\n遲下屌柒大交合都未遲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌柒外敵先<br />\n<br />\n皇家香港天文台點衰都係自己人"},{"pid":"aac4b0b876b7aeffed24d0c70051bff7d0fc5ddd","tid":383526,"uid":103230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T16:11:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>為左笑澳門抬高香港大交合咩玩法</blockquote><br />\n笑撚左班垃圾澳狗先<br />\n遲下屌柒大交合都未遲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌柒外敵先<br />\n<br />\n皇家香港天文台點衰都係自己人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只求唔好晦辱皇家一詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e09cece73041889e8f40f7ffd135e4b05179669","tid":383526,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T16:11:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>為左笑澳門抬高香港大交合咩玩法</blockquote><br />\n笑撚左班垃圾澳狗先<br />\n遲下屌柒大交合都未遲</blockquote><br />\n大交合起碼方法係科學，只不過決定有政治/經濟考慮<br />\n澳門就連科學都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d535db5ebeda081d87560d2d6c0a85fbd56347f","tid":383526,"uid":78385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T16:19:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/02/001856_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F02%2F001856_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=d86a33d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最update 澳門連波邊都摸唔到<br />\n仲好意思掛風球"},{"pid":"72deaf4058bc37f4299f68fa07cea0c32e400f57","tid":383526,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T05:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170902/large/1504290912_b228.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170902%2Flarge%2F1504290912_b228.png&h=9c20036f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【0300更新】瑪娃由昨晚8時開始，轉向西北偏西緩慢移動，進入本港400公里範圍。<br />\n<br />\n【0230更新】天文台稍為調強今日的風勢預測，由昨午僅料風勢和緩（3至4級），惟今晨發出，1號波後，改料今日稍後風勢清勁（5級），與昨晨的預測相約。<br />\n<br />\n【0225更新】天文台指，瑪娃凌晨轉向西北移動，稍為靠近廣東東部沿岸，並逐漸增強，故在凌晨2時20分發出一號戒備信號，而因瑪娃移動較慢，本港日間風勢不會顯著增強，黃昏前改發三號強風信號的機會較低，但隨着瑪娃明日於汕尾以東登陸，香港今明兩日間中有狂風驟雨，呼籲市民安排戶外活動時，應留意最新天氣情況。<br />\n<br />\n【0220】<br />\n南海東北部的熱帶氣旋「瑪娃」，昨日日間的路徑不似預期，一直北漂，令區內多個氣象部門大跌眼鏡，紛紛東調預測路徑，其中香港天文台料瑪娃明晚（3日）在距離香港更遠的汕頭至汕尾一帶登陸，即本港以東200公里左右掠過，登陸前或只能增強為強烈熱帶風暴，或颱風下限。<br />\n<br />\n因瑪娃的路徑較預期遠離本港，天文台昨午亦調弱本港今明兩日的風雨預測；由昨晨預測今日稍後「驟雨增多」，明日「密雲，有狂風大驟雨，吹強風（6至7級）」，至昨午的預測已調弱為今日稍後僅「雨勢有時較大」，明日僅「多雲，有狂風驟雨，風勢和緩至強風程度（5至6級）」，但仍勉強達3號風球標準。"},{"pid":"2a9d3e34b0b618143147c74ba9ff6586cba5f979","tid":383526,"uid":38523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T05:38:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>柒得過D連登仔</blockquote><br />\n柒得過支那五毛狗？"},{"pid":"21abaf96043eab78f4af0fdd7c8dfa86b2f93303","tid":383526,"uid":107210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:25:47.000Z","msg":"完美演譯咩叫五十步笑一百步 不用笑 大家都是中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ae278d6a40bfe3cdaf5a044ccb4d08e62184143","tid":383526,"uid":2613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:19:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>為左笑澳門抬高香港大交合咩玩法</blockquote><br />\n笑撚左班垃圾澳狗先<br />\n遲下屌柒大交合都未遲</blockquote><br />\n大交合起碼方法係科學，只不過決定有政治/經濟考慮<br />\n澳門就連科學都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大交合預測路經都幾準既<br />\n只係掛波要睇商家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c07b7823029d93ab9f46ed57ee00a535718d26b6","tid":383526,"uid":2613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T04:13:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f969a90c18b53560b20db417926f3750f89d1e9","tid":383526,"uid":69187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T04:55:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73db96892bbeb48a9e22bdc454eba080e9747b8a","tid":383526,"uid":2613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T00:58:55.000Z","msg":"binc<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}